So this

00:10:38.919 --> 00:10:41.999
soul which is made of the five causal bodies

00:10:42.069 --> 00:10:43.919
and your centers,

00:10:44.939 --> 00:10:48.999
plus we can say, also

00:10:52.029 --> 00:10:56.959
it has got the control over the parasympathetic,

