and they saw it under a microscope when I told them,

00:12:31.079 --> 00:12:39.039
that the soul within us is reflected on the cell,

00:12:39.989 --> 00:12:44.039
which is the reflector of every cell.

00:12:44.899 --> 00:12:48.049
So the part of the cell which is the reflector,

00:12:49.039 --> 00:12:56.069
which is placed on one side of the cell

