also has this soul reflected,

00:13:05.109 --> 00:13:09.989
and the main soul which is on the back

00:13:10.089 --> 00:13:12.119
controls that

00:13:17.059 --> 00:13:21.939
reflected soul which looks after every cell.

00:13:22.069 --> 00:13:26.939
Now they have found out that there is in that reflector

00:13:27.919 --> 00:13:30.989
this kind of seven loops,

00:13:31.069 --> 00:13:34.879
seven loops because it sits on the eight –

00:13:35.999 --> 00:13:38.919
seven chakras and the Mooladhara.

00:13:40.989 --> 00:13:43.029
Now what He found out that,

00:13:43.899 --> 00:13:45.059
when people die

00:13:45.899 --> 00:13:47.099
then some of the souls

