are born again just after few days,

00:13:57.939 --> 00:14:01.919
and these people are just very ordinary type of people,

00:14:02.009 --> 00:14:05.969
that's how He brought in a kind of category.

00:14:06.059 --> 00:14:09.099
So they are - the people who have died -

00:14:10.089 --> 00:14:13.949
they are of a category, one category,

00:14:14.019 --> 00:14:20.079
where they exist for a very short time

00:14:21.109 --> 00:14:23.119
in the collective subconscious

00:14:23.939 --> 00:14:25.099
and then they take their rebirth.

00:14:32.899 --> 00:14:34.939
They are very ordinary people,

00:14:35.029 --> 00:14:37.099
aimless, useless people.

00:14:38.899 --> 00:14:41.049
But there are some souls when they die,

00:14:41.909 --> 00:14:43.119
they just hang in the air

00:14:43.929 --> 00:14:46.099
and they are just waiting to find out somebody

00:14:46.929 --> 00:14:50.059
who will fulfill their desires

00:14:50.889 --> 00:14:52.989
which are not yet fulfilled.

