00:16:03.109 --> 00:16:06.939
I remember of a lady who was a very short, petite person,

00:16:06.999 --> 00:16:07.999
came from Cuba,

00:16:08.089 --> 00:16:10.109
in America when I went first,

00:16:10.109 --> 00:16:14.049
and she told Me that she's very sick of herself.

00:16:14.899 --> 00:16:16.939
And her husband told Me that she can take

00:16:17.009 --> 00:16:21.949
one whisky bottle, full, neat sometimes.

00:16:22.939 --> 00:16:25.939
Looked at her, such a little thing. I said "How can she do it?"

00:16:27.039 --> 00:16:34.929
So, I put a bandhan on her and I saw a huge big Negro

00:16:34.999 --> 00:16:36.109
standing behind her.

00:16:36.969 --> 00:16:38.919
So I said, "Do you know some Negro?"

00:16:38.999 --> 00:16:40.949
Immediately she jumped on Me. She said,

00:16:41.009 --> 00:16:42.069
"Mother, You see that one?

00:16:42.899 --> 00:16:45.889
You see that one, that's the one drinks, not me."

00:16:46.969 --> 00:16:49.099
Of course I cured her

00:16:49.909 --> 00:16:51.959
and after that she gave up drinking completely.

00:16:52.049 --> 00:16:58.909
So whenever you start getting into a habit in a bad way,

00:16:59.899 --> 00:17:02.979
you lose complete control of yourself

00:17:03.079 --> 00:17:08.029
and a spirit sits on you, and it controls you.

00:17:10.889 --> 00:17:12.029
And when it controls you,

00:17:13.009 --> 00:17:16.909
you do not know how to get rid of any habit.

00:17:16.999 --> 00:17:19.899
That's why it's difficult to get rid of habits.

00:17:19.959 --> 00:17:22.949
Now in Sahaja Yoga when the Kundalini rises what happens

00:17:23.989 --> 00:17:27.959
that these spirits, these dead spirits

00:17:28.029 --> 00:17:31.039
leave you and you become all right and you give up.

00:17:31.099 --> 00:17:32.939
